
UPDATE course_modules 
SET content_md = content_md || E'\n\n### What makes Claude different from ChatGPT?\n\nMany lawyers have tried ChatGPT and been disappointed. Claude is built differently:\n\n| Feature | Claude | ChatGPT |\n|---|---|---|\n| Context window | 200K tokens (~150 pages) | 128K tokens |\n| Legal accuracy | Higher precision, fewer hallucinations | More creative, less precise |\n| Safety training | Constitutional AI approach | RLHF approach |\n| Document analysis | Excellent at long documents | Better at short tasks |\n\n:::info\n**For legal professionals**, Claude''s ability to process entire contracts, briefs, and case files in a single conversation is a game-changer. No more splitting documents into chunks.\n:::\n\n### Your first week with Claude\n\nHere''s what to focus on:\n1. **Day 1-2**: Practice basic prompts (summaries, drafting)\n2. **Day 3-4**: Try document analysis with real (non-confidential) documents\n3. **Day 5**: Set up a Claude Project for a practice area\n\nBy the end of this module, you''ll understand *what* Claude can do. The next modules will show you *how* to do it brilliantly.'
WHERE id = 'fa0ddbf5-253a-4047-b8e6-051b88bf130b';
